title: Second.In.Command.2006.STV.DVDSCR.XVID-COBRA
description: Jean-Claude Van Damme plays an official who&#039;s just been appointed as Second In Command to the U.S.Ambassador at an American Embassy in a small, turbulent Eastern European nation.When local insurgents attempt a coup d&#039;etat, the nation&#039;s President takes refuge inside the embassy.The embassy is then besieged by the well-armed insurgents.The U.S. Ambassador is killed in the ensuing action, an now it&#039;s up to Jean Claude and the embassy&#039;s small detachment of U.S. Marines to fend off the attackers
